@strmppl: jdownloader is a program for automatized download of the files from file-sharing servers. .dlc is a file he can use and where links in encrypted form are stored.
It is a must have. Just do Google - write down in Search bar a word jdownloader. It is free, well known program and used by millions for years.

Do the same on Youtube, many tutorials in many languages is available there - if your connection is too slow to watch them on-line, use Firefox browser and Download Helper extension for browser and save those video-guides for off-line watching.

Thank you.

@valu59er: I wish that you more frequently write your comments. I am sick worried about some of you, especially now when lilars is gone.

@all: "Thanks" is not just a matter of my own vanity, nor can substitute a true gratitude - but it is a written confirmation "I am right here" from many of you I know for years. We never met eachother, but it gives me (and to you guys) some sense of community and belonging to something bigger.
